Package items

Enum Class ItemTemplate

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ItemTemplate>
items.ItemTemplate
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ItemTemplate>, Constable
public enum ItemTemplate extends Enum<ItemTemplate>
The ItemTemplate enum represents different types of items in the game. Each item has a name, type, weight, and maximum value.
